snippet.title: Nickelodeon All-Star Brawl: Catdog vs. Lucy Gameplay
snippet.description:
Check out gameplay of Catdog facing off against The Loud House's Lucy Loud in Nickelodeon All-Star Brawl, the fighting game due out this Fall for PlayStation platforms, Xbox platforms, Nintendo Switch, and PC.
